channel.title: Renewable Energy - Azure Onyxscore [Drum & Bass]
channel.description:
[Renewable Energy - Azure Onyxscore](https://soundcloud.com/azureonyx/renewable-energy)
I'm almost done with this album, which is taking 2 years to make already. wish me luck, one more track to go.
A little bit of history, this track was made around the time when [Interstate 5](https://soundcloud.com/auxycollective/interstate-5) was created, back in 2019, which is why the intro may sound familiar if you've been listening to Auxy Collective's megacollabs.
